{"tid":2342013,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(鬼滅劇透慎入) 大家喜歡九柱邊個","createTime":"2020-12-26T19:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T06:16:08.000Z","uid":224966,"like":12,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"658189893d8f91360f670eabd02eb1b2e3da2d23","tid":2342013,"uid":224966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T19:06:32.000Z","msg":"個人喜歡水柱同炎柱<br />\n<br />\n水柱個反差萌好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為好cool但內心勁錫男主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中後段唔講以為佢想同炭治朗搞基<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n炎柱就唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />令人聯想起艾斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n煉獄san完美演繹咗炎屬性特質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想睇煉獄san開斑紋到底幾熱血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f65336640fbc95b98d6aa7639c23f4b33b285c","tid":2342013,"uid":333199,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T19:16:32.000Z","msg":"拳柱"},{"pid":"9bd289ebc07c01a3edb26890f2220b78c99aeb54","tid":2342013,"uid":144683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T20:42:58.000Z","msg":"岩柱"},{"pid":"41393beeac3341c9427907ae6cdcb6b98b055887","tid":2342013,"uid":35406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T21:12:10.000Z","msg":"頭柱"},{"pid":"b0aa7dddac3557bafa4e623361014a4b3853b5e7","tid":2342013,"uid":117357,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T21:56:20.000Z","msg":"台灣洪秀柱"},{"pid":"f780e4df7f12b4c9782bf3a448c0ef45e8ce5bc7","tid":2342013,"uid":384604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T21:58:46.000Z","msg":"岩柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想俾佢瘋狂抽插<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable